From d5ccd5d21291de46586ab2cd1e7d08318325ba81 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: dominicg <dominicg@brax3.local>
Date: Thu, 16 Jul 2026 07:19:16 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] brax3: add MTK ATCI + meta_tst provisioning blobs

Restore the vendor blobs backing the re-enabled proprietary-files
entries so snWriter (META/AT) and the Engineering Mode backend work:

  bin/meta_tst, bin/atcid, bin/audiocmdservice_atci
  etc/init/atcid.rc, etc/init/audiocmdservice_atci.rc
  lib64/vendor.mediatek.hardware.atci@1.0.so
  lib64/libhfmanagerwrapper.so, libwifical.so, libwifinvram.so
  lib64/libkmsetkey.so, libwifitest.so

The five libs are transitive MTK dependencies of meta_tst/atcid; the
audio HAL deps of audiocmdservice_atci resolve transitively through the
in-tree libaudioprimarydevicehalifclient. Blobs sourced from the BSP
vendor image (mgvi_64_ww_armv82). Android.bp and brax3-vendor.mk
regenerated via extract-utils.

Co-Authored-By: Oz <oz-agent@warp.dev>
Change-Id: I8457ca1df55c9fc6e0cb6a1ae45649cdc89a9f86
